{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, Robledo and Zuluaga (2022) conducted a bibliometric analysis of TM studies published until November 13, 2021.",
    "Since then, this field has witnessed significant growth in terms of the development of large language models 1 3 (LLMs) applied to build neural topic models.",
    "For example, BERTopic (Grootendorst 2022; Ogunleye et al. 2023).",
    "More recent studies like Abdelrazek et al. (2023) and Wu et al. (2024) reviewed TM studies in terms of methods, applications, and challenges specific to the neural topic models.",
    "However, these recent studies ignored the bibliometric analysis of the TM field."
  ]
}